data.description: Look no further! This beautifully upgraded 4/3.5 is right off exit 9 making it minutes away from everything. Property was built in 2021. upgraded floors, Lighting, Yard, and little details throughout makes it anyones dream home. This spacious home also offers a large backyard with space for your own pool or entertaining friends and family. Oversized driveway fits 4+ Cars. High end vinyl floors 100% waterproof, Recessed lighting, 6x6 wood Pergola with concrete slab and turf design.All baseboards and doorframes are flat modern style. 2 Bedrooms have full bathrooms inside. 2021 Build Home. Upgraded Refrigerator.
